    <item>
      <title>据称阿达尼计划为旗舰公司融资 12 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/billionaire-adani-said-to-plan-raising-1-2-billion-for-flagship</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，亿万富翁高塔姆阿达尼 (Gautam Adani) 的旗舰公司正考虑通过出售股票筹集约 1000 亿卢比（12 亿美元）至 1200 亿卢比，此前他的电力传输部门刚刚完成了另一项融资交易。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/billionaire-adani-said-to-plan-raising-1-2-billion-for-flagship</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 10:44:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>波动带来机遇：Kevin Mahn</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-07/with-volatility-comes-opportunity-kevin-mahn-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Hennion &amp; Walsh Asset Management 首席投资官 Kevin Mahn 表示，美联储下次降息的不确定性造成了不可预测性和短期波动。他补充说，投资者需要意识到人工智能是一场长期博弈，人们不应该放弃大型科技股，并表示这可能需要几个季度，但回报会到来。他在彭博简报上与 Manus Cranny 进行了交谈。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-07/with-volatility-comes-opportunity-kevin-mahn-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 10:40:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>CVS 再次下调预期，启动 20 亿美元成本削减计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/cvs-slashes-outlook-again-launches-2-billion-cost-cutting-plan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[CVS Health Corp. 股价下跌，原因是该公司连续第三个季度下调了 2024 年盈利预期，并宣布了削减成本的措施，以在医疗费用持续飙升的情况下在未来几年内节省 20 亿美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/cvs-slashes-outlook-again-launches-2-billion-cost-cutting-plan</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 10:30:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马士基船舶订单表明人们对液化天然气作为船用燃料的看法发生了变化</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/maersk-s-big-ship-order-includes-liquefied-gas-fueled-vessels</link>
      <description><![CDATA[航运巨头马士基航运公司 (A.P. Moller-Maersk A/S) 目前正在采购 50 至 60 艘船只作为其船队更新计划的一部分，其中包括能够使用液化天然气 (该公司过去曾批评过这种燃料) 运行的船只。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/maersk-s-big-ship-order-includes-liquefied-gas-fueled-vessels</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 07:29:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国经济放缓危及中国出口驱动型复苏之路</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/us-economy-imperils-china-path-of-exporting-its-way-to-recovery</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国的出口引擎对于保持中国实现5%左右的增长目标至关重要，但现在，美国需求下滑的迹象正对出口造成威胁，而北京方面也在努力提振自身的消费经济。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/us-economy-imperils-china-path-of-exporting-its-way-to-recovery</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本央行鸽派信号削弱进一步加息预期 日元下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/yen-extends-losses-against-dollar-as-market-volatility-continues</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本央行副行长内田新一表示，如果金融市场不稳定，政策制定者将不会进一步提高基准利率，随后日元大幅下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/yen-extends-losses-against-dollar-as-market-volatility-continues</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 01:49:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
